(148, 1, '2015-08-02 17:07:33', '2015-08-02 17:07:33', 'Mission Quest Advertising is a Pro-Military promotional products distributor who services all Military Branches and Commercial industries. Mission Quest was established in 2011 and is located in Bradenton, Florida. We understand the commitment for Quality Products with a fast Delivery Time. Our team takes pride in our Customer Service as we are a company you can count on to get the job done. We also back our business with a 100% satisfaction policy.\r\n\r\nOur goal is to provide our customers with high quality promotional items which will increase your brand awareness among your target audience and strengthen your brand identity within your market. Our Commitment is to our Troops &amp; fellow Americans in assisting promotional needs as we are dedicated to “Targeting your Market”. Not only do we supply promotional items, we are a creative marketing group who brings new and innovative ideas to the table. We simplify the ordering process and believe in the concept of taking care of the people who take care of us.\r\n\r\nKeep in mind our website is only a small fraction of the products we supply. If for some reason you can’t find what you’re looking for on our website, contact us at the office to speak with a Representative and let us do the work for you.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to working with you.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2015-09-10 19:45:46', '2015-09-10 19:45:46', '', 0, 'http://missionquest.dev/api/?page_id=148', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(149, 1, '2015-08-02 17:07:33', '2015-08-02 17:07:33', 'Located in Bradenton, Florida, Mission Quest Advertising is a promotional product supplier who services all branches of the Military and Commercial industries. With over 10 years of industry experience, we understand the commitment for Quality products, fast delivery, and most of all the Customer Service you can rely on to get the job done.  Our goal is to provide our customers with high quality promotional items which will increase your brand awareness among your target audience and strengthen your brand identity within your market. Our Commitment is to our Troops &amp; fellow Americans in assisting promotional needs as we are dedicated to “Targeting your Market”.\r\n\r\nMission Quest Advertising offers our customers a wide range of promotional products for every occasion. We specialize in providing creative ideas of promotional goods for special events such as Weddings, Banquets, Golf Outings, fundraisers and tradeshows. We also understand the lifespan of promotional products and the marketing impact these products have to the end user. Promo items have a much longer lifespan than that of traditional forms of advertising and studies have shown that these items result in a more positive attitude toward the company as a whole. Our team of professionals understands this and works together with our customers to provide better innovative ways to increase your brand familiarity with quality products to fit within your budget.\r\n\r\nOur website is only a small fraction of the products we supply. If for some reason you can’t find what you’re looking for on our website, contact us at the office to speak with a Representative and let us do the work for you.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-02 17:07:33', '2015-08-02 17:07:33', '', 148, 'http://missionquest.dev/api/148-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
